              Instructions

Can you draw a line from the white
 square at the bottom to the pale blue
 one at the top without hitting the
 coloured shapes?

To draw the line you must tell the
 arrow how to move.
Type f1 for forward 1 dot,
 (f2=forward 2 dots etc.)
To turn a corner type l for left and
 r for right.
After each order press RETURN to start
 a new order.
You can try again if you crash into a
 shape or do not hit the target.

PRESS ANY KEY TO CONTINUE